OL,3,CWest Brom sack boss after failing to
OL,4,Cwin a single game in charge
OL,6,FWest Bromwich Albion sacked their head
OL,7,Fcoach, Eric Ramsay, after he failed to
OL,8,Fwin any of his nine games in charge.
OL,10,FThe 34-year-old from Shrewsbury took
OL,11,Fcharge at the Hawthornes on the 11th
OL,12,Fof January on a two-and-a-half-year
OL,13,Fcontract.
OL,15,FThe club announced Ramsay's sacking
OL,16,Fafter his side drew 1-1 with Charlton
OL,17,Fin the Championship.
OL,19,FHe leaves the club one point above the
OL,20,Frelegation zone with 10 matches left
OL,21,Fto be played this season.
