OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772012404
OL,3,CWest Brom sack boss after failing to
OL,4,Cwin a single game in charge
OL,6,FIn a statement, West Bromwich Albion
OL,7,Fsaid: "West Bromwich Albion have
OL,8,Fparted company with men's first team
OL,9,Fhead coach Eric Ramsay.
OL,11,F"Assistant head coach Dennis Lawrence
OL,12,Fhas also departed The Hawthorns.
OL,14,F"The club would like to place on
OL,15,Frecord its thanks to Eric and Dennis
OL,16,Fand wishes them well for the future."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
