PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772012404
OL,3,CWest Brom sack boss after failing to
OL,4,Cwin a single game in charge
OL,6,FRamsay joined West Brom after a spell
OL,7,Fin charge of Minnesota United in the
OL,8,FUnited States, during which he guided
OL,9,Fthem to the semi-finals of the Major
OL,10,FLeague Soccer play-offs. Before then,
OL,11,Fhe had worked alongside Manchester
OL,12,FUnited manager Eric Ten Hag in 2024.
OL,14,FHe has also worked as an assistant
OL,15,Fcoach for Wales and spent time with
OL,16,FSwansea, Shrewsbury and Chelsea,
OL,17,Fthough his playing experience extends
OL,18,Fonly to a short spell with Welshpool
OL,19,FTown and international futsal for
OL,20,FWales.
